Interface AuxiliaryCasField

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface AuxiliaryCasField
extends QuizzesField
    Field for the auxiliary Computer Algebra System field to be shown in the response form or in the review page of a question. This object is always built from QuizzesComponentBuilder.
